#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/ebay_connector/setup.rst:95
msgid ""
"**List**/ **Link**: generate a new eBay listing with an Odoo product by "
"clicking :guilabel:`List Item on eBay` or :guilabel:`Link With Existing eBay"
